message: Hey! Are you free to chat?
Sure, what's up?
Just wanted to check in and see how things are going.
All good here! How about you?
I'm doing well, just busy with work.
I get that! Same here.
By the way, did you see the latest episode?
Yes! It was amazing!
I can’t believe the twist at the end.
Right?! I didn’t see that coming at all.
Let's grab a coffee this weekend?
Sounds good! Saturday morning?
Perfect. See you then!
Did you finish the project?
Almost done, just adding the final touches.
Great! Let me know if you need any help.
Thanks! I’ll keep you posted.
Hey, can you send over the files from last week?
Of course, sending them now.
Got them, thanks!
